Megatron looked astonishdly at Firestrike. He was almost dissapointed,
for if he could have got the old Firestrike to understand, he could have
a very powerful warrior, of both mind, and body. But right now he was
more curious as to what was going on. Somebody had to have mettled with
Firestrike's mind, otherwise he was badly dammaged to continued acting
so strange. "Enter the ship." He commanded, as he thought of how to deal
with it.
